.npm init to install package.json it will not work as react like npm install 
.then after package.json create in cmd : npm install chalk to create a node module (read properties of chalk from npm website)
.now create a.mjs file and import chalk from 'chalk' and use it as importing so .mjs file is used for ES6 module system.
.now in package.json add "type":"module" to use .js file as ES6 module system.
now in cmd: npm install express to create express module and use it in  file as ES6 module system.
.then : npm i is-odd to install is-odd module and use it in file as ES6 module system. to check whether number is odd or even. like import isOdd from 'is-odd'; console.log(isOdd(3)); // true
